{"about_the_game":"You are a dwarven smith, looking to reclaim lost homeland. Forge the means to achieve this task as you move through the caves. Dig up precious metals - each with unique properties - and craft your masterpiece using modular inventory system. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/extras/about-crafting.gif?t=1717933983\" /><br><br>Forge axe blades, pickaxe heads, gun barrels, hooks and many more. Experiment with different materials, explore synergies between them, choose right weapon archetype and fuse them as you wish!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/extras/about-fight.png?t=1717933983\" /><br><br>Battle through multiple floors of cavernous passages and dwarven fortress rooms. Along the way you will find traps and treasures, enemies big and small and many, many ore deposits ripe for the taking.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/extras/about-mining.png?t=1717933983\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural level generation with multiple biomes<br></li><li>20+ different weapon enhancing materials and special parts<br></li><li>Axes, pickaxes, hammers, hooks, guns and other weapon archetypes available to fuse together<br></li><li>Interactable environment that can be used against you or your enemies<br></li><li>Many enemy types, including powerful bosses to face off against </li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717933983","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1717933983","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891760/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1717933983","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akama